SetString english backpack "Backpack"
SetString english backpack_base "base"
SetString english backpack_base_description "."
SetString english backpack_carter "Carter-A259"
SetString english backpack_carter_description "Backpack worn by the spartan known as Carter-A259."
SetString english backpack_cortana "The Package"
SetString english backpack_cortana_description "Don't make a girl a promise... if you know you can't keep it."
SetString english backpack_jetpack "jetpack"
SetString english backpack_jetpack_description "Out of comission."
SetString english backpack_jorge "Jorge-052"
SetString english backpack_jorge_description "Backpack worn by the spartan known as Jorge-052."
SetString english backpack_jun "Jun-A266"
SetString english backpack_jun_description "Backpack worn by the spartan known as Jun-A266."
SetString english backpack_marine "Rucksack"
SetString english backpack_marine_description "Most UNSC combatant personnel carry rucksacks in the field to store small items and mat\u00e9riel for their personal use."
SetString english backpack_mp_dutch "ODST (Dutch)"
SetString english backpack_mp_dutch_description "Worn by Corporal Taylor H. Dutch Miles of Alpha-Nine."
SetString english backpack_mp_mickey "ODST (Mickey)"
SetString english backpack_mp_mickey_description "Worn by Corporal Taylor H. Mickey Miles of Alpha-Nine."
SetString english backpack_mp_rookie "ODST (Rookie)"
SetString english backpack_mp_rookie_description "Standard Issue Orbital Drop Shock Trooper Utility Backpack."
SetString english backpack_odst "odst"
SetString english backpack_odst_description "All-purpose hardened storage."
SetString english backpack_orion "Orion"
SetString english backpack_orion_description "Shoulder Angel, micro-missile/decoy launcher."
SetString english backpack_radio "radio"
SetString english backpack_radio_description "Standard UNSC radio transmission pack."
SetString english backpack_raven2 "odst (HVY)"
SetString english backpack_raven2_description "As they say during ODST screening: the best defense is an overwhelming offense."
SetString english backpack_raven3 "odst (COMM)"
SetString english backpack_raven3_description "The ensemble for an ODST that wants to reach out and touch someone with artillery and ortillery support."
SetString english backpack_raven4 "odst (DEMO)"
SetString english backpack_raven4_description "Obstacles to progress are measured by the number of satchel charges they rate."
SetString english backpack_reentry "M-Spec reentry pack"
SetString english backpack_reentry_description "The M-Spec Reentry Pack, also known as the Reentry Unit, is a piece of UNSC equipment. The reentry pack is integrated into the YSS-1000 Sabre, hooking onto the pilot's back as soon as they enter."
SetString english body "Body Type"
SetString english bottom_helmet_flair "Bottom HeadGear"
SetString english bottom_helmet_flair_base "base"
SetString english bottom_helmet_flair_base_description "The Command Network Module allows users to communicate and synchronize with the UNSC battle network in real-time.[2] Different base variants has been observed across branches and ranks within the UNSC, including UNSC Army troopers, Orbital Drop Shock Troopers, and Spartans."
SetString english bottom_helmet_flair_cbrn "cbrn"
SetString english bottom_helmet_flair_cbrn_description "The Command Network Module allows users to communicate and synchronize with the UNSC battle network in real-time.[2] Different cbrn variants has been observed across branches and ranks within the UNSC, including UNSC Army troopers, Orbital Drop Shock Troopers, and Spartans."
SetString english bottom_helmet_flair_hul "hul"
SetString english bottom_helmet_flair_hul_description "The Command Network Module allows users to communicate and synchronize with the UNSC battle network in real-time.[2] Different hul variants has been observed across branches and ranks within the UNSC, including UNSC Army troopers, Orbital Drop Shock Troopers, and Spartans."
SetString english bottom_helmet_flair_scarf1 "scarf"
SetString english bottom_helmet_flair_scarf1_description "Even Spartans get cold."
SetString english bottom_helmet_flair_scarf2 "scarf secondary"
SetString english bottom_helmet_flair_scarf2_description "Even Spartans get cold."
