SetString english r_forearm "Right Forearm"
SetString english r_shoulder "Right Shoulder"
SetString english right_helmet_flair "Right HeadGear"
SetString english right_helmet_flair_1_hul "hul-1"
SetString english right_helmet_flair_1_hul_description "The Hardened Uplink (hul-l) is an external helmet attachment compatible with helmet variants of the MJOLNIR Powered Assault Armor."
SetString english right_helmet_flair_base_flair "base"
SetString english right_helmet_flair_base_flair_description "."
SetString english right_helmet_flair_cnm "cnm"
SetString english right_helmet_flair_cnm_description "The Command Network Module or CNM, is a communication device utilized by the United Nations Space Command, commonly adopted as an external helmet attachment."
SetString english right_helmet_flair_hu/rs "hu/rs"
SetString english right_helmet_flair_hu/rs_description "The hardened uplink/remote sensor package (HU/RS) is an external helmet attachment, which integrates the Hardened Uplink with a remote sensor into a single attachment, employed by the United Nations Space Command."
