SetString english top_helmet_flair "Top HeadGear"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_aug "aug"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_aug_description "The Command Network Module allows users to communicate and synchronize with the UNSC battle network in real-time. [2] Different aug variants has been observed across branches and ranks within the UNSC, including UNSC Army troopers, Orbital Drop Shock Troopers, and Spartans"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_ba "hu"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_ba_description "The Command Network Module allows users to communicate and synchronize with the UNSC battle network in real-time. Different CNM variants has been observed across branches and ranks within the UNSC, including UNSC Army troopers, Orbital Drop Shock Troopers, and Spartans"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_base "base"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_base_description "The Hardened Uplink (base) is an external helmet attachment compatible with helmet variants of the MJOLNIR Powered Assault Armor."
SetString english top_helmet_flair_binoculars "binoculars"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_binoculars_description "Different binoculars variants has been observed across branches and ranks within the UNSC, including UNSC Pilot troopers."
SetString english top_helmet_flair_cnm "cnm"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_cnm_description "The Command Network Module allows users to communicate and synchronize with the UNSC battle network in real-time. [2] Different CNM variants has been observed across branches and ranks within the UNSC, including UNSC Army troopers, Orbital Drop Shock Troopers, and Spartans"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_fc "fc"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_fc_description "The Command Network Module allows users to communicate and synchronize with the UNSC battle network in real-time. [2] Different CNM variants has been observed across branches and ranks within the UNSC, including UNSC Army troopers, Orbital Drop Shock Troopers, and Spartans"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_hul "hul"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_hul_description "The Command Network Module allows users to communicate and synchronize with the UNSC battle network in real-time. [2] Different CNM variants has been observed across branches and ranks within the UNSC, including UNSC Army troopers, Orbital Drop Shock Troopers, and Spartans"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_i "i"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_i_description "The Command Network Module allows users to communicate and synchronize with the UNSC battle network in real-time. [2] Different CNM variants has been observed across branches and ranks within the UNSC, including UNSC Army troopers, Orbital Drop Shock Troopers, and Spartans"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_nxra "nxra"
SetString english top_helmet_flair_nxra_description "The Command Network Module allows users to communicate and synchronize with the UNSC battle network in real-time. [2] Different nxra variants has been observed across branches and ranks within the UNSC, including UNSC Army troopers, Orbital Drop Shock Troopers, and Spartans"
